During the afternoon a messenger delivered the prints to the pictures they had made the previous day. None was missing nor were there any deletions.\par
Evening came with its violent flare of color. Paddy and Fay stacked their equipment on the dilapidated old air-boat, rose over Aevelye, took off for Fumighast Ventrole.\par
Over the mouth of the hole the guard ship pulled up alongside.\par
The same corporal saluted them, glancing at their makeshift equipment with contemptuous amusement.\par
